Frederic D. SUMMERALL, Appellant, v. UNITED FRUIT COMPANY, Appellee. No. 214. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. Jan. 6, 1936. For opinion below, see 11 F.Supp. 963. Simone D. Gazan and Gazan & Caldwell, all of New York City, for appellant. W. Dale Williams, of New York City (Roscoe H. Hupper and A. Howard Neely, both of New York City, of counsel), for appellee.

Before L. HAND, SWAN, and AUGUSTUS N. HAND, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Order affirmed.
